edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc78268ff870f9f6792c3c00ecb73bbdc9d7a77","tid":89139,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:30:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.cmd.gov.hk/html/b5/important_info/alert.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmd.gov.hk%2Fhtml%2Fb5%2Fimportant_info%2Falert.html&d=%2FAH5SopbTphPa9NB3QF7xYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=aaa92c9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.cmd.gov.hk/html/b5/important_info/alert.html</a>"},{"pid":"bb60f5815488ee74101ef861ee3a7a8f73ff36bf","tid":89139,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:35:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">強國毒物4次封王後, 於2011年應已封聖, 以後將不會將強國毒物所佔的百分比公佈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/193047_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F193047_fd4c8e59b8a7add298869bd9fef2417c.jpg&h=fca8c78d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"http://www.dh.gov.hk/tc_chi/pub_rec/pub_rec_ar/pub_rec_arpis_previous.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dh.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Fpub_rec%2Fpub_rec_ar%2Fpub_rec_arpis_previous.html&d=%2FAH5SopbTphPa9NB3QF7xYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=7452423c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dh.gov.hk/tc_chi/pub_rec/pub_rec_ar/pub_rec_arpis_previous.html</a><br />\n<br />\n越搵越多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06781dd9034a5338ee5fc82eaa97a4e2ffbd391b","tid":89139,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:43:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2dc1db837f4487780405e0c731687cd7a19905b0","tid":89139,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:41:39.000Z","msg":"烏頭類中藥類用得咁撚粗疏，真係隨時死人。<br />\n呢類藥一定要極小心炮製過，先至可以入藥，問題係，啲藥喺邊到炮製？咪鬼國囉。咁已經完全無保障無信心。<br />\n就算炮製咗，使用份量過大(每個人都唔同)，一樣會食死人。香港中醫質素係點？算撚數啦。<br />\n咁執藥嗰批呢？是但讀幾個月就話有執藥牌，隨時生熟附子都未識份，搞錯咗又死得。有啲仆街又懶醒，厘碇都唔用，話自己隨手執都啱份量，烏頭類執錯少少都夠食死個客。<br />\n你有無睇過中醫張執藥方，鬼畫符咁睇撚錯份量一啲都唔出奇。<br />\n好喇，當全部無出錯，包藥正正常常到咗個客手，你監唔監管到個客？<br />\n如果個客係睇慣中醫就仲大劑。一般感冒藥煲半個鐘就得，佢慣咗攞包有烏頭藥嘅又煲佢半個鐘就飲，佢唔中毒我跟佢姓。<br />\n太撚大機會出現人為錯誤，喺香港呢個咁嘅環境之下用烏頭藥，根本就係搞笑。"},{"pid":"e12bc4079ae2957ffbc502d2847dca1453dcb779","tid":89139,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c74bff1a26726f4e7d111114b33d9c290085396c","tid":89139,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd80b4d025bb23249468fd6551224f6252b15ac","tid":89139,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烏頭類中藥類用得咁撚粗疏，真係隨時死人。<br />\n呢類藥一定要極小心炮製過，先至可以入藥，問題係，啲藥喺邊到炮製？咪鬼國囉。咁已經完全無保障無信心。<br />\n就算炮製咗，使用份量過大(每個人都唔同)，一樣會食死人。香港中醫質素係點？算撚數啦。<br />\n咁執藥嗰批呢？是但讀幾個月就話有執藥牌，隨時生熟附子都未識份，搞錯咗又死得。有啲仆街又懶醒，厘碇都唔用，話自己隨手執都啱份量，烏頭類執錯少少都夠食死個客。<br />\n你有無睇過中醫張執藥方，鬼畫符咁睇撚錯份量一啲都唔出奇。<br />\n好喇，當全部無出錯，包藥正正常常到咗個客手，你監唔監管到個客？<br />\n如果個客係睇慣中醫就仲大劑。一般感冒藥煲半個鐘就得，佢慣咗攞包有烏頭藥嘅又煲佢半個鐘就飲，佢唔中毒我跟佢姓。<br />\n太撚大機會出現人為錯誤，喺香港呢個咁嘅環境之下用烏頭藥，根本就係搞笑。</blockquote><br />\n咁咩環境下用先唔搞笑"},{"pid":"8f2007c22ec2fd5185c3d88c9d7bc99eee61f4a5","tid":89139,"uid":1291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"垃圾中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a992a2bb89a7aa7a46fdd6a0f5e5a02c8a96e6ea","tid":89139,"uid":47153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:40:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔超出藥典標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪繼續跟啲藥典囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66e06e5557967b916cbc859f5470fdc22080ce2","tid":89139,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T13:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6ad5cb26cf80ee3d7c98f984e685136ec3968e","tid":89139,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T16:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}